### Get all published events
GET {{base_url}}/events

### Get first published event
GET {{base_url}}/events/first

### @name create_event
POST {{base_url}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{org_token}}

{
  "title": "Tech Meetup",
  "description": "A meetup for developers",
  "date": "2025-12-15T18:00:00Z",
  "location": "Paris",
  "capacity": 50,
  "status": "published"
}

### Get event by ID
GET {{base_url}}/events/{{event_id}}

### Update event (organizer)
PUT {{base_url}}/events/{{event_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{org_token}}

{
  "title": "Tech Meetup - Updated",
  "capacity": 100
}

### Register for event (member)
POST {{base_url}}/events/{{event_id}}/register
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### Unregister from event (member)
DELETE {{base_url}}/events/{{event_id}}/register
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### Delete event (organizer)
DELETE {{base_url}}/events/{{event_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{org_token}}

### Delete event (admin)
DELETE {{base_url}}/events/{{event_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
